proc originaldata

Manual page for proc_originaldata(PL)

DESCRIPTION

proc originaldata may be used to inform subsequent plotting procedures that the original data set is to be used, rather than the results of a previous proc tabulate (or proc processdata where stack was used)

ATTRIBUTES

None.

EXAMPLE

#proc originaldata
